lead_paragraph: European golfers have endured a 17-year title drought at the Masters after dominating the tournament for two decades, a barren run that three-times winner Nick Faldo says can only be explained by "cycles".

headline.print_headline: Europe's Masters Drought Down to 'Cycles': Faldo
